===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# An [[advantage]], [[help]] or [[aid]].
# A [[payment]] made in [[accordance]] with an [[insurance]] [[policy]] or a [[public]] [[assistance]] [[scheme]].
# A [[performance]], etc, given to [[raise]] [[fund]]s for some [[cause]].

====Synonyms====
*(''advantage, help''): [[advantage]], [[aid]], [[assistance]], [[boon]], [[help]]
*(''payment''): [[subsidy]]

====Antonyms====
*(''advantage, help''): [[disadvantage]], [[encumbrance]], [[hindrance]], [[nuisance]], [[obstacle]]

